# Caddy reverse proxy for rightcourtsc.com — Phase 6 of planning/07-VPS-MIGRATION.md
# Install to /etc/caddy/Caddyfile on the VPS (provision.sh does this), then:
#   systemctl reload caddy
# Caddy obtains and renews TLS automatically. DNS for rightcourtsc.com (and www) must
# already point at this box before Caddy can issue certificates.

rightcourtsc.com {
	reverse_proxy 127.0.0.1:3000
	encode zstd gzip
}

www.rightcourtsc.com {
	redir https://rightcourtsc.com{uri} permanent
}
